name: XCTWaiter.Result
desc: Result states returned by a waiter when it completes, times out, fails, or is interrupted.

items.name: case completed
items.desc: All of the waiter’s expectations were fulfilled successfully.

items.name: case timedOut
items.desc: The waiter timed out before all of its expectations were fulfilled.

items.name: case incorrectOrder
items.desc: The waiter’s expectations were not fulfilled in the required order.

items.name: case interrupted
items.desc: The waiter was interrupted prior to its expectations being fulfilled or timing out.
